                <div style="font-size:12px; margin-top:6px">Teacher Lab - in - Charge</div>
              </td>
              <td style="padding:8px; font-size:11px;">
                <ol style="padding-left:16px; margin:0;">
                  <li>1.) Reservation must be done three (3) days prior to its use. Use of laboratory is only up to 6:00 pm and beyond it needs special arrangement due to the READS schedule.</li>
                  <li>2.) CLAYGO (Clean As You Go)! Cleaning of Lab & its utensils specially in the Caregiving, H.E. & BPFM Laboratory is the responsibility of the one who reserves it. CPR Mannequins, tools & utensils should not be brought outside the Lab unless properly reserved.</li>
                  <li>3.) If READS is not available, please put off the lights, Air-con and other electrical devices in the laboratory. Thank You!</li>
                </ol>
              </td>
              <td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:bottom; padding:8px;">
                <div style="border-top:1px solid #000; width:80%; margin:0 auto;"></div>
                <div style="font-weight:700; margin-top:6px">Mr. Adrian A. Adlaon</div>
                <div style="font-size:12px">T.L.E Subject Area Chairman</div>
              </td>
            </tr>
